               \"readObject\",\n                    MethodType.methodType(void.class, ObjectInputStream.class));\n        }\n        catch (IllegalAccessException | NoSuchMethodException e) {\n            throw new ExceptionInInitializerError(e);\n        }\n    }\n\n    private static BCECGOST3410PublicKey createPublicKey() {\n        ECNamedCurveParameterSpec curve = ECGOST3410NamedCurveTable.getParameterSpec(CURVE_NAME);\n        ECNamedCurveSpec parameters = new ECNamedCurveSpec(\n                CURVE_NAME,\n                curve.getCurve(),\n                curve.getG(),\n                curve.getN(),\n                curve.getH(),\n                curve.getSeed());\n        org.bouncycastle.math.ec.ECPoint generator = curve.getG().normalize();\n        ECPoint publicPoint = new ECPoint(\n                generator.getAffineXCoord().toBigInteger(),\n                generator.getAffineYCoord().toBigInteger());\n        return new BCECGOST3410PublicKey(new ECPublicKeySpec(publicPoint, parameters));\n    }\n\n    private static byte[] serialize(Object value) throws Exception {\n        ByteArrayOutputStream output = new ByteArrayOutputStream();\n        try (ObjectOutputStream objectOutput = new ObjectOutputStream(output)) {\n            objectOutput.writeObject(value);\n        }\n        return output.toByteArray();\n    }\n\n    private static byte[] readEncodedObject(byte[] serializedObject) throws Exception {\n        try (ObjectInputStream inputStream = new ObjectInputStream(new ByteArrayInputStream(serializedObject))) {\n            return (byte[])inputStream.readObject();\n        }\n    }\n\n    private static final class EncodingObjectOutputStream extends ObjectOutputStream {\n        private final ByteArrayOutputStream outputStream;\n\n        private EncodingObjectOutputStream() throws Exception {\n            this(new ByteArrayOutputStream());\n        }\n\n        private EncodingObjectOutputStream(ByteArrayOutputStream outputStream) throws Exception